Text: Your Scottrader Authorization CodeThank you for Registering with Scottrader Your UserID is your valid email address which you provided during the registration process Your unique Authorization Code is OPF This authorization code is issued by Scottrader and cannot be changed by the user Please make note of your authorization code and save this email for future reference Users must register with Scottrader in order to access our free real time streaming quotes Do not allow others to use your authorization code as this may result in loss of your usage privileges We appreciate the opportunity to serve you Click here to Log In to Scottrader now Tell a Friend about Scottrader Click here scottradeqtreferasp to tell your friends about this exciting FREE service To learn more about Scottrade visit Scottradecom At Scottrade market orders are just PLUS with branch offices nationwide theres a local branch office near you to service your account Click here locationsasp to find your local branch office Scottrader is a free service of Scottradecom Memeber SIPC Click here privacyhtm to read our privacy policy
